Rating: 4
Excellent! Used a whole calico bass and micro steam it. Used chopped green onions instead of shallots. Seasoned cavity with salt & pepper, sprinkle some green onions and thinly sliced lemons in cavity. Added slice lemons on top of the fish. Cover with plastic wrapped and micro cook 5 mins on high, then turned fish over and 3 mins more. Sprinkled pecan green onion topping. Served with basmati rice. Yum!

